    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You need big integer arithmetic. JavaScript implements integers as 32 bit ints (`2^32`). It's very likely that your balance in wei exceeds that number:\n\n```\n> eth.getBalance(eth.coinbase)\n1.2230537249418869769081e+22\n```\n\nTry something like\n\n```\neth.getBalance(eth.coinbase).sub(eth.gasPrice).mul(....)\n```\n",
